01. Install Atom/VScode
02. installing node.js and node version manager
03. Install MongoDB - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FwMwO8pXfq0
04. Install Postman
05. Install nodejs package with npm
  - open cmd
  - goto desired new folder
  - npm init
  - npm install readline-sync --save
  - npm install package.json
  - npm install --save express body-parser mongoose
  
  
run a normal node.js file

go to termianl - node <file_name>
               - node app.js
               
